i have been hooked onto this song! 
Emotionally i haven’t been at my best since the past
2-3 months and the last week has not been the best.
Letting go, moving on, feeling better and breaking down again has what the past few days have looked like. Tomorrow is June 1, a new month and starting it with a good energy is my intention. Hope June brings stability and peace. Admist all of this watching or listening anything related to Radha-Krishna made me feel so much better, it gave the calm to my chaos!
Words can’t put out but things felt better. ❤️

latestPosts.caption:
all my life I have struggled with my relationship with food! I have been a big foodie at heart but also someone who wants to be fit. However I kept on juggling between these two aspects of my personality and it turned out that I chose extremes of both , when I used to eat healthy it was stricter than ever and if I break the diet I eat whatever in any portion I feel like. I missed the balance & whenever I overate , I felt miserable. In this I always “ALMOST” reached my dream body because whenever I lost control I used to eat whatever and however. Anyways now that I am growing up and being softer to myself I understand that taking care of my body but still eating my favourite foods. Its okay to overeat , we are privileged for overeating and the bloat that you hate is a sign of privilege. BE GRATEFUL ❤️ 

#reels #fyp #relatable #relationshipwithfood #reelsinstagram #thoughts #lifethoughts #grateful
